  "tn5726a177": "We offer Trial Packs and Variety Packs so you can sample our products before committing to full size. We strongly encourage and promote buying a Trial Pack as this should usually eliminate the need for a return.  If you purchase a full size product or tub for any reason and sample from it, it is not eligible for a return, refund or exchange for any reason, including but not limited to an allergic reaction.  Trial Packs, Trial Pack Bundles, Sample Packs are final sale items and cannot be returned for any reason.",
  "tn23ead1f": "We strongly believe in our products and want to make sure you are satisfied. If you are not completely satisfied with an 'unopened' product (seals intact) purchased directly from DevotionNutrition.com, notify us within 15 days from the date of purchase. Dependent on the circumstances you may be responsible for return shipping.  Upon receipt of your products, a refund of the product purchase price, less any discounts used at checkout and a 10% restocking fee, will be issued.  Shipping charges will not be refunded unless there was an error on the part of Devotion Nutrition.",
  "tn220257ff": "Devotion Nutrition cannot accept returns of opened products (broken seal).",
  "tn6dfe827b": "If you purchased your products from somewhere other than DevotionNutrition.com, please contact the store or website you purchased from and they can help you with your return.",
  "tn1dba7bcd": "Return Descriptions:",
  "tn70956357": "Devotion Nutrition is not responsible for lost, stolen, or damaged items.  OrderProtection.com covers your order for every major issue that can occur during shipping. Your order will be protected against loss, damage, theft, wrong items, defective items and missing items. If something goes wrong during shipping, you can ",
  "t721c8acc": "quickly file a claim in a few clicks",
  "t208abf45": ". You'll receive a refund or reshipment if your claim is approved.  To protect your order, make sure Order Protection is toggled on in your cart.",
  "t3b9be956": "Trial and/or Sample Packs:  We do not accept returns or offer refunds on any trial packs or trial pack bundles, in full or in part, for any reason whatsoever.",
  "tn4b5fc54c": "Wrong Product(s) sent: If you received the wrong products please let us know within 15 days. We apologize and will immediately send you the correct products and send out a return shipping label to receive back the incorrect item(s).",
  "t16d7aa8e": "Change of Heart: If you would like to return an unopened product (tamper seal intact) due to a change of heart we will gladly take it back. You must report it within 15 days and have it shipped back.  Upon receipt of your products, a refund of the product purchase price, less any discounts used at checkout and a 10% restocking fee, will be issued.  Shipping charges will not be refunded unless there was an error on the part of Devotion Nutrition.",
  "t5879b822": "Allergic Reaction: We strongly encourage and promote buying a Sample Pack as this should usually eliminate the need for a return.  If you purchase a full size product or tub for any reason and sample from it, it is not eligible for a return, refund or exchange for any reason, including but not limited to an allergic reaction.  ",
  "tn639e3a06": "For any return questions or concerns please email ",
